valent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>relatedEntity.relatedPerson</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPersonneStructure.personne.IdentitePersonne.nomPersonne</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>relatedEntity.relatedPerson.name.family</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPersonneStructure.personne.IdentitePersonne.prenomPersonne</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>relatedEntity.relatedPerson.name.given</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPersonneStructure.personne.IdentitePersonne.civilite</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>relatedEntity.relatedPerson.name.prefix</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMPersonneStructure.personne.IdentitePersonne.titre</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>relatedEntity.relatedPerson.name.suffix</td></tr></table><hr/><p><b>Group 2 </b>Mapping from <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-related-entity</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-related-person-document</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Source Code</b></td><td><b>Relationship</b></td><td><b>Target Code</b></td></tr><tr><td>relatedEntity</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>RelatedPerson</td></tr><tr><td>relatedEntity@classCode</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #efefef\">(not mapped)</td></tr><tr><td>relatedEntity.code</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>RelatedPerson.r